<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤١٠٣ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/474">‌ابْنُ السَّرْحِ </a>قَالَ: رَأَيْتُ فِي كِتَابِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3332">‌خَالِي، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4444">‌عُقَيْلٍ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">‌ابْنِ شِهَابٍ </a>بِإِسْنَادِهِ وَمَعْنَاهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>